                     <interp inst="t17991030-31-off174" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17991030-31-off174" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17991030-31-cd175" type="crimeDate">20th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17991030-31-off174 t17991030-31-cd175"></join>, a pair of pistols, value 21s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17991030-31-victim318" type="victimName">
                     John 
